fluorite crystals,

271
00:12:59,750 --> 00:13:01,750
but that's not a problem here.

272
00:13:01,958 --> 00:13:03,875
There's more than enough
by the sea in Barcelona.

273
00:13:04,083 --> 00:13:05,500
FLUORITE ACQUIRED!!

274
00:13:06,041 --> 00:13:09,458
