good at math.

327
00:15:12,458 --> 00:15:13,583
Ha ha.

328
00:15:13,791 --> 00:15:15,875
I want their computational
skills.

329
00:15:16,083 --> 00:15:17,208
It's the only way
we're going to get

330
00:15:17,416 --> 00:15:19,000
the precise calculations we

331
00:15:19,208 --> 00:15:21,000
need for our big moon mission.

332
00:15:21,208 --> 00:15:22,250
Yeah.

333
00:15:22,250 --> 00:15:24,083
Well, seems we're
going to India.

334
00:15:24,291 --> 00:15:25,333
Huh?

335
00:15:25,541 --> 00:15:26,833
Wait a minute,
don't forget we're

336
00:15:27,041 --> 00:15:28,500
all the way over in Spain.

337
00:15:28,500 --> 00:15:31,041
How the heck are we going
to get to India from here?

338
00:15:31,250 --> 00:15:33,125
We'll have to make
a lengthy trip to go

339
00:15:33,333 --> 00:15:35,916
