340
00:15:36,125 --> 00:15:36,916
That's bad.

341
00:15:37,125 --> 00:15:38,375
[RYUSUI] Thing is,

342
00:15:38,583 --> 00:15:40,291
we've got a little issue

343
00:15:40,500 --> 00:15:42,041
to solve with the new
Perseus before we

344
00:15:42,250 --> 00:15:44,875
can start our voyage to India.

345
00:15:45,083 --> 00:15:48,291
We're burning through
fuel faster than expected.

346
00:15:48,500 --> 00:15:50,333
At this rate, we
won't make it there.

347
00:15:50,541 --> 00:15:52,083
Not without more fuel.

348
00:15:53,333 --> 00:15:54,458
Don't sweat it.

349
00:15:54,666 --> 00:15:56,125
It would honestly
be way freakier

350
00:15:56,333 --> 00:15:58,500
if science always worked
out perfectly, you know.

351
00:15:58,708 --> 00:16:01,166
Well, I guess we'll be
making a lot more fuel

352
00:16:01,375 --> 00:16:03,125
out of organic waste, huh?

353
00:16:03,333 --> 00:16:05,708
[RYUSUI] Looks like that
is the whole reason we

354
00:16:05,916 --> 00:16:07,958
installed our own fuel plant.

355
00:16:08,166 --> 00:16:10,250
But we're stuck here
until we have enough,

356
00:16:10,458 --> 00:16:13,250
