to happen anytime soon.

357
00:16:13,458 --> 00:16:16,125
It could take months
or even a year.

358
00:16:16,333 --> 00:16:18,041
[gasps]

359
00:16:19,125 --> 00:16:20,125
Hold on.

360
00:16:20,333 --> 00:16:21,416
It looks like the water

361
00:16:21,625 --> 00:16:22,916
connects through this part.

362
00:16:23,125 --> 00:16:24,833
If we can slip through
that skinny opening,

363
00:16:25,041 --> 00:16:26,625
we're in the clear, right?

364
00:16:26,833 --> 00:16:28,291
It's a bad shortcut.

365
00:16:28,500 --> 00:16:31,416
You can't tell me that won't
solve our fuel problem.

366
00:16:31,625 --> 00:16:34,041
That spot is called
the Suez Canal.

367
00:16:34,250 --> 00:16:37,125
It was carved by mankind
to connect the two seas

368
00:16:37,333 --> 00:16:39,000
