389
00:17:14,500 --> 00:17:16,041
This is our chance
for a grudge match

390
00:17:16,250 --> 00:17:18,166
against those canal things.

391
00:17:19,333 --> 00:17:21,166
I'm not big on waiting.

392
00:17:21,375 --> 00:17:23,875
A huge part of me
wants to go for it.

393
00:17:24,083 --> 00:17:27,125
That said, as captain,
I have to refuse.

394
00:17:27,333 --> 00:17:29,583
We don't even know
if it's still connected.

395
00:17:29,791 --> 00:17:32,166
If we charge in blind
without a sea map,

396
00:17:32,375 --> 00:17:35,583
