end and never make it back.

397
00:17:35,791 --> 00:17:37,041
Am I wrong?

398
00:17:37,250 --> 00:17:38,541
Way too bad we can't take

399
00:17:38,750 --> 00:17:40,333
a little peeksy before leaving.

400
00:17:40,541 --> 00:17:42,250
We do have the world's
all-time greatest

401
00:17:42,458 --> 00:17:43,833
geographer at our disposal.

402
00:17:44,041 --> 00:17:46,083
You trying to make
me blush over here?

403
00:17:46,291 --> 00:17:48,791
If only Chelsea could get
a good look at it from far away

404
00:17:49,000 --> 00:17:50,958
