of super-powered telescope

405
00:17:51,166 --> 00:17:52,583
or something like that.

406
00:17:52,791 --> 00:17:53,875
Huh?

407
00:17:56,125 --> 00:17:59,833
[triumphant music]

408
00:18:05,541 --> 00:18:09,291
[adventure music]

409
00:18:24,583 --> 00:18:27,291
[CHELSEA] This view
is fantabulous.

410
00:18:27,500 --> 00:18:28,916
It's primo supremo.

411
00:18:28,916 --> 00:18:31,166
I can make a whole ass sea
chart of the Suez Canal

412
00:18:31,375 --> 00:18:32,500
no biggie.

413
00:18:32,500 --> 00:18:34,916
Well, how's it
looking from up there?

414
00:18:35,125 --> 00:18:36,750
Can we make it
through the canal,

415
00:18:36,958 --> 00:18:38,833
