off like we thought?

416
00:18:40,041 --> 00:18:41,750
Scribble, scribble, scribble,
scribbe, scribble,

417
00:18:41,958 --> 00:18:43,750
scribble, scribble.

418
00:18:46,833 --> 00:18:49,041
It's got a hardcore blockage.

419
00:18:50,208 --> 00:18:53,208
Our errible-tay
luck strikes again.

420
00:18:55,250 --> 00:18:56,208
Hold up.

421
00:18:56,416 --> 00:18:57,500
Weird alert.

422
00:18:57,708 --> 00:18:59,291
It's def super whack,

423
00:18:59,500 --> 00:19:01,708
