439
00:19:35,416 --> 00:19:38,291
We can't sail the ship
there until the dam's gone.

440
00:19:40,000 --> 00:19:41,166
Basically,
you're saying we're

441
00:19:41,375 --> 00:19:42,458
going to need a nasty

442
00:19:42,666 --> 00:19:44,000
