445
00:19:48,291 --> 00:19:49,458
Can we do it?

446
00:19:49,666 --> 00:19:51,416
I'm afraid to ask.

447
00:19:51,625 --> 00:19:54,083
[lively music]

448
00:19:55,500 --> 00:19:56,583
THE TEAM FIGURES IT OUT

449
00:19:56,791 --> 00:19:58,541
Please tell me
you're oking-jay.

450
00:19:58,750 --> 00:19:59,875
This can't be real.
- Huh?

451
00:20:00,083 --> 00:20:01,291
THE VILLAGE TEAM
