our first rocket together.

462
00:20:29,583 --> 00:20:31,416
Ignition.

463
00:20:31,625 --> 00:20:35,750
[whooshing]

464
00:20:38,833 --> 00:20:43,041
[chuckles]

465
00:20:53,208 --> 00:20:55,958
Do your thing, rocket.

466
00:20:56,166 --> 00:20:58,166
[whooshing]

467
00:20:58,375 --> 00:20:59,958
Ha ha.

468
00:21:00,166 --> 00:21:03,208
