472
00:21:18,625 --> 00:21:20,125
Okey dokey.

473
00:21:26,375 --> 00:21:29,125
[smashing noise]

474
00:21:31,375 --> 00:21:32,708
Booyah!

475
00:21:32,916 --> 00:21:36,166
You took a major L, Suez Canal.

476
00:21:36,375 --> 00:21:37,500
