477
00:21:37,708 --> 00:21:39,416
We're taking a huge shortcut.

478
00:21:39,625 --> 00:21:40,833
[RYUSUI] Ha ha.

479
00:21:41,041 --> 00:21:44,208
Now we can set course
straight to India.

480
00:21:44,416 --> 00:21:45,916
I still don't get
why we're going.

481
00:21:45,916 --> 00:21:49,875
