to find in this India place?

482
00:21:50,083 --> 00:21:52,125
Excellent question, Kohaku.

483
00:21:52,333 --> 00:21:54,083
We know how to make
a rocket now,

484
00:21:54,291 --> 00:21:57,250
but we still need India's
mathematical prowess.

485
00:21:57,458 --> 00:21:59,458
Once we find a way
to get precise trajectory

486
00:21:59,666 --> 00:22:02,208
