off to visit Why-man.

487
00:22:02,416 --> 00:22:03,541
Hell yeah.

488
00:22:04,625 --> 00:22:06,083
[RYUSUI] We're after
the final puzzle

489
00:22:06,291 --> 00:22:07,916
