mind for mathematics.

491
00:22:11,875 --> 00:22:14,083
I know just the person.

492
00:22:14,291 --> 00:22:16,708
Humanity's almighty
mathematician.

493
00:22:18,583 --> 00:22:21,791
[theme music]

494
